    "Cogitated", "Crunched", "Pondered", "Ruminated", "Brewed",
    "Simmered", "Composed", "Crafted", "Forged", "Hatched",
    "Computed", "Percolated", "Synthesized", "Manifested", "Harmonized",
    "Architected", "Crystallized", "Orchestrated", "Calibrated", "Channeled",
    "Deliberated", "Noodled", "Contemplated", "Incubated", "Germinated",
